body:
I got a flow that has `endColumn` as `0`. This is invalid and breaks the SARIF report.

The code in question is at https://github.com/nextcloud/server/blob/66013f906d1957bdc9de1851a0f7497fbc5bbfbf/apps/federation/lib/Controller/OCSAuthAPIController.php#L144. Lines 163 to 167 are the violating ones with `endColumn` as `0`. Could be related to the array syntax:

```
		$this->jobList->add(
			'OCA\Federation\BackgroundJob\GetSharedSecret',
			[
				'url' => $url,
				'token' => $token,
				'created' => $this->timeFactory->getTime()
			]
		);
```
